<subSubSection pageId="199" pageNumber="477" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="199.[1378,2589,1912,2457]" pageId="199" pageNumber="477">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1383,1518,2187,2220]" pageId="199" pageNumber="477">Breeding.</emphasis>
Most reproductive activity of Unicolored Grass Mice occurs in November— January. Highest proportion of shedding individuals was found in autumn and winter.
</paragraph>
